{"tid":761433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎改圖 陳恒鑌：目前供應未穩　改善後歡迎內地人來港打疫苗 (14:33)","createTime":"2018-07-30T11:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T11:35:35.000Z","uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d2cd69cea2c3a0125379ec9cf618751991532d","tid":761433,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:31:14.000Z","msg":"內地官媒《環球時報》指，低門檻、獨特區位優勢及認同香港疫苗安全，讓「赴港打疫苗」成為近年內地人赴港旅遊其中一項選擇。本港民建聯立法會議員陳恒鑌直言，歡迎內地客來香港打疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n陳恒鑌接受《環球時報》訪問時表示，內地人來港打疫苗近年很普遍，「尤其近期，內地人赴港打疫苗的諮詢量出現明顯增長」。不過他指出，在藥企保持香港市場供應穩定下，「對內地客人到香港打疫苗持歡迎態度」，因對香港旅遊經濟有益。<br />\n<br />\n陳恒鑌又說，香港疫苗斷貨壓力一直存在，主要集中在私人醫療機搆。不過，他又說，不認為香港私人醫療機構疫苗短缺壓力源自內地人或中介機搆，重申香港疫苗是否短缺，主因是藥廠能否穩定供應，「這是由藥企的商業運作決定」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180730/s00001/1532927779505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180730%2Fs00001%2F1532927779505&d=%2BgVoHcd6%2BMNZKlRJSTTeFwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=230884cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180730%2Fs00001%2F1532927779505&h=676611ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180730/s00001/1532927779505</a>"},{"pid":"031c798cac1e5951f020895b2f3cf1eea9420470","tid":761433,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/193230_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F193230_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f75ec8f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d83ed4e7180023fff148403c3cc5f725f1d6ded9","tid":761433,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"唔該去哂屯門天水圍元朗打<br />\n<br />\n益返佢啲選區"},{"pid":"36b92c395e7db3a10747057039ff2fc5394676b9","tid":761433,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"嚟打囉，我見一個打一個"}]}